               <p>
            
               
                  <persName id="t16880113-4-defend25" type="defendantName">
                     Thomas 
                     Westmoreland
                  <interp inst="t16880113-4-defend25" type="surname" value="Westmoreland"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16880113-4-defend25" type="given" value="Thomas"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16880113-4-defend25" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
            , a <rs id="t16880113-4-deflabel15" type="occupation">Boy</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t16880113-4-defend25 t16880113-4-deflabel15"></join>, was Indicted for <rs id="t16880113-4-off16" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t16880113-4-off16" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16880113-4-off16" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing in the Parish of <placeName id="t16880113-4-crimeloc17">St. Brides</placeName>
                     <interp inst="t16880113-4-crimeloc17" type="placeName" value="St. Brides"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16880113-4-crimeloc17" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                     <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t16880113-4-off16 t16880113-4-crimeloc17"></join>, an Alamode Silk Hood, value 6 s.
            </rs> from 
               
                  <persName id="t16880113-4-victim27" type="victimName">
                     William 
                     Hawley
                  <interp inst="t16880113-4-victim27" type="surname" value="Hawley"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16880113-4-victim27" type="given" value="William"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16880113-4-victim27" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t16880113-4-off16 t16880113-4-victim27"></join>
                  </persName>
               
             
                  <rs id="t16880113-4-viclabel18" type="occupation">Milliner</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t16880113-4-victim27 t16880113-4-viclabel18"></join>, on the <rs id="t16880113-4-cd19" type="crimeDate">29th. of December</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t16880113-4-off16 t16880113-4-cd19"></join> last; the Prosecutor followed him and took the Goods upon him, he having took the Hood off the Stall. The Boy could say nothing but that he found it dropt in the Court: He was brought in <rs id="t16880113-4-verdict20" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t16880113-4-verdict20" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16880113-4-verdict20" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder1s"></interp>
               guilty to the value of 10 d.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t16880113-4-punish21" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t16880113-4-punish21" type="punishmentCategory" value="corporal"></interp>
